All the fields are self-explanatory, but the following fields may need clarification:
</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>
Initial offset: some acquisition systems record the data with a fixed offset.
</para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>
Voltage range: the total voltage range, e.g. if the system is set to Â±5V, the range is 10V.
</para>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</sect1>
